The paper focuses on the technical aspects of autonomous driving, specifically tracking, prediction, and decision making. These topics are closely related to robotics (cs.RO), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and control systems (cs.SY). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
